message: Hello! Thank you for contacting Better Deal Insurance. My name is Chris. How can I assist you today?
I have been trying to get in touch with someone from your company for days now! Your service is terrible!

I'm deeply sorry to hear about the trouble you've faced trying to reach us. I completely understand your frustration. Let's get to the bottom of this. Before we proceed, can you confirm your full name for security purposes?
Thank you for confirming. Your date of birth, please?
Great, thank you. Just one more thing, could you please provide your first line of address and postcode?
Perfect! Thank you for completing security. How can I assist you today, John?
I've been trying to make a claim for my car insurance, but your website keeps crashing every time I try to submit the form. This is unacceptable!

I'm sorry to hear about the trouble you've faced with our website. That must be really frustrating. Let's work together to find a solution. One possible resolution could be for me to assist you with submitting your claim manually. Would that work for you?
Yes, please! I need to get this claim submitted as soon as possible

Of course, I can help with that. Thank you for allowing me to assist you. Let's get started on submitting your claim. Please provide me with the details, and I'll make sure it's taken care of. I'm glad that I was able to help.
Thank you, Chris. I appreciate your help.
You are welcome, John. If you need any further assistance or have any other concerns, please don't hesitate to let me know. Have a great day!
